template2
=========

Object name:
------------
expected: foo
got:      {{ name }}

Object type:
------------
expected: foo
got:      {{ kind }}

field1 value
------------
expected: foo_value_1
got       {{ obj.field1 }}

field2 value
------------
expected: foo_value_2
got       {{ obj.field2 }}

bar.field1 value
-----------------
expected: bar_value_1
got       {{ obj.bar.field1 }}

bar.field2 value
-----------------
expected: bar_value_2
got       {{ obj.bar.field2 }}


glabal variable
---------------
expected: blabla_value
got:      {{ globals.blabla.field }}
